THERE WERE BUT **THIRTEEN** GENERATIONS FROM ABRAHAM TO DAVID.

Abraham begat Isaac . . . Jacob . . . Judas . . . Phares . . . Esrom . .
. Aram . . . Aminaldab . . . Naason . . . Salmon . . . Booz . . . Obed .
. . Jesse . . . David .. \[13\]. (Matt. 1:2, 3, 4, 5, 6.)

 

<span id="an_68">68</span>.

