So David bought the threshing floor and the oxen for *fifty shekels of
silver*. (2 Sam. 24:24.)

DAVID BOUGHT THE THRESHING FLOOR FOR **SIX HUNDRED** SHEKELS OF GOLD.

So David gave to Oman for the place *six hundred shekels of gold*. (1
Chron. 21:25.)

 

